WorkItem.Description:
When selecting a div tag by id the div tag inner text is correct:
 
HtmlNode all_tab = doc.GetElementbyId("ALL_TAB");
 
When using either of these xpath statements to select nodes, the number of nodes matches the number of nodes that match the query in the entire document, not in the subset represented by all_tab:
 
HtmlNodeCollection failure_nodes = all_tab.SelectNodes("//b[contains(.,'Failure')]");
HtmlNodeCollection exception_nodes = all_tab.SelectNodes("//b[.='Failure']");
